&lt;li&gt;Design layouts and aesthetic features for basic architectural assignments&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Coordinate drawings and specifications with the specification writer and assist in preparing some sections&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Apply DLR Group practice standards to project assignments and develop comprehensive design and technical skillsets for material and construction techniques&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Participate in innovative idea generation within the team to achieve design excellence&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Understand and apply BIM standards to projects and develop organized work sets according to DLR Group standards&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Execute QA/QC procedures, resolve clash detection issues, and review and address comments from third-party QA/QC reviews&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate actively with the project team to generate design ideas and solutions&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Communicate effectively with project team members through written, oral, and visual means&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Seek new knowledge and skills by asking questions of peers and proactively share potential solutions&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Deliver project work on schedule to meet overall project deadlines and understand project work plans and target deadlines for each task&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
