&lt;li&gt;Evaluate the impact and feasibility of energy conservation strategies through optimization of building form, envelope, electrical and mechanical systems.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Apply their knowledge of building systems and critical thinking skills to troubleshoot technical design challenges.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Research high performance building strategies such as daylight optimization, thermal comfort, analysis of metered data, etc.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Act as an integrated design resource, providing insights and actionable data to project teams to set and achieve building performance goals.&lt;/li&gt;
