&lt;li&gt;Leading Integrated Design charrettes managing and providing sustainable design services during different phases of the design process.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Advocate within the firm on the topics of building performance and sustainable design.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Possess knowledge of the practical application of advanced techniques in energy modeling.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Perform Energy and Life Cycle Analysis for the different energy conservation measures.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Perform Measurement and Verification services for post occupancy evaluation.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide support to teams to meet Architecture 2030 targets.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Advocate for Architecture 2030 and support reporting both inhouse and within the building community.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Advocate within the firm on the topics of building performance and sustainable design.&lt;/li&gt;
